                                TASK 3

3.1 
recruit@umuzi:~/workspace$ touch umuzi.md
recruit@umuzi:~/workspace$ touch recruits.md
recruit@umuzi:~/workspace$ touch cohort.md

3.2
recruit@umuzi:~/workspace$ cat > umuzi.md
Boitumelo
^Z
[1]+  Stopped                 cat > umuzi.md

recruit@umuzi:~/workspace$ cat > recruits.md
Smart and Beautiful
^Z
[2]+  Stopped                 cat > recruits.md
recruit@umuzi:~/workspace$ cat > cohort.md
Brave and Bold
^Z
[3]+  Stopped                 cat > cohort.md


3.3
recruit@umuzi:~/workspace$ cat umuzi.md recruits.md cohort.md
Smart and Beautiful
Brave and Bold
Smart and Beautiful
Brave and Bold

3.4
recruit@umuzi:~/workspace$ touch summary.md
recruit@umuzi:~/workspace$ cat umuzi.md recruits.md cohort.md > summary.md

3.5
recruit@umuzi:~/workspace$ cat >> summary.md
THE END
^Z
[4]+  Stopped                 cat >> summary.md
recruit@umuzi:~/workspace$ cat summary.md
Smart and Beautiful
Brave and Bold
Smart and Beautiful
Brave and Bold
THE END


